Packages
Package Description
bot
The package containing the Main class for starting the bot.
bot.debugger
The package containing the logic behind the debugger.
bot.ui.table
The package containing UI classes for the debugger.
callbacks
The package containing callbacks from the patched OpenRSC JAR.
compatibility.sbot
The package containing code for SBot compatability.
controller
The IdleScript API package.
listeners
The package containing various listeners which are constantly running as separate threads from the main bot.
models.entities
The package containing ground item and skill definitions for the debugger.
reflector
Container package for the Reflector class.
scripting.idlescript
The package where IdleScript scripts go.
scripting.sbot
The package where SBot scripts go.
